<title>aria2</title>
<p>This page explains all options for configuring aria2 in Preferences in <app>Parabolic</app>.</p>

<terms>
    <item>
        <title>Usa aria2</title>
        <p>If enabled, Parabolic will use aria2c to download media.</p>
        <p>Although using aria2c can improve download speed, download progress will not be displayed in the UI.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Predefinito: Disattivato</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
